items.title: Humberto grows to major hurricane in the Atlantic. Maps show its forecast path.
items.description: Humberto rapidly strengthened into a major hurricane as it churned over the Atlantic Ocean, the National Hurricane Center said.

items.title: Midtown Manhattan mass shooting gunman had low-stage CTE, medical examiner finds
items.description: Shane Tamura, the gunman who killed four people in a deadly Midtown Manhattan shooting, had low-stage CTE, officials said Friday.
